description:
Today we take desserts to the next level with some JOLLY French specialties courtesy of a Michelin-star chef! Get your Jolly merch at http://getjolly.store 

Massive thanks to chef Thibault Sombardier and the team at Les Parisiens for showing us a whole new world of exquisite puddings! Check them out if you're in Paris:

Les Parisiens: https://www.instagram.com/restaurant_les_parisiens/
Thibault Sombardier: https://www.instagram.com/thibaultsombardier/

Click here to buy Josh's bestselling autobiography! https://amzn.eu/d/73xtwcy

Hit join and become a Jollybean member to join us in our members-only livestreams:
https://www.youtube.com/jolly/join

Special thanks to our Jollybean VIPs for supporting us in making this video!
